::DarkMouse::

"Thank you my commander. You are too kind."
She got up off the floor and walked over to Scorponok.
She looked at him and felt ashamed.  She had insulted her high commander in 
front of another commander.  She wanted to go and hide.  She could hardly 
look into Scorponok's eyes.  She just looked at the floor.
She whispered to Scorponok, "I'm sorry."
She didn't know what else to say.  She knew that she was very lucky this 
time round.  But she knew that she would have to watch herself in the 
future. She just looked at the floor.  She felt to ashamed to look into her 
beloved's eyes.
